{
  "stem": "131.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was that time-- that was already in '38-- my brother was in Spain, and he sent us papers that we should-- the whole family, my mother and all my sisters-- we should leave.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my mother didn't want to leave her parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No way that she would go somewhere without her parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why was he?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was studying architecture in France, and I don't know why he went at that time to Spain from France.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He married there a French girl, born in Paris, already, but from Polish people, Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know why he went to Spain, but in Spain he invented the neon sign the first time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes because we locked every door, and they knocked on the doors always at night and screamed, open the door.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what they could take, what they saw without asking from the tables-- candelabras, or whatever was silver there, without asking they took out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't say even boo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lots of time when we came from school-- not just me, we came always in bunches-- and it was a pleasure for them to beat us, to give us slaps some time that you can fall down for no reason at all, just to hurt us.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was the worst time because I was a young girl, 15 year old, and I needed friends and needed to go out, not to stay in the house constantly.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They felt the same way, but we were afraid even to talk about things because they just came and banged on the doors all time, or broke even windows sometimes, just for kicks.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes they didn't even come in, just broke the windows for us to scare us.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
